Some fancy footwork with CoreData. Objectives are to showcase support for a majority of the functions that CoreData provides. The data model is reasonably simple while demonstrating all the intricacies of CoreData.

 - Validation support.
 - Undo management.
 - Transient properties and NSManagedObject life cycle usage.
 - Faulting.
 - Cache Invalidation.
 - KVO of core data properties.
 - Multi threading support.